text: It took us two hours to ‘march’ (shuffle) the length of this street and 90 minutes more to send this tweet. I’d say this is at least 2 or 3 times as crowded as the first anti Brexit march I covered as a reporter 2 years ago when the same distance took about half an hour. – bei Piccadilly Circus
